AncestralWarriorTotemPlayer.description: Raise a Totem that uses socketed Mace Skills. Cannot use Channelling Skills or Skills with Cooldowns.
AncestralWarriorTotemPlayer.name: Ancestral Warrior Totem

ArmourBreakerPlayer.description: Strike with a forceful blow, knocking enemies back and weakening their Armour.
ArmourBreakerPlayer.name: Armour Breaker

ArmourPiercingBoltsAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with a clip of bolts that can be fired rapidly and Break enemy Armour. Using this skill again reloads the clip.
ArmourPiercingBoltsAmmoPlayer.name: Load Armour Piercing Rounds

ArmourPiercingBoltsPlayer.description: Rapidly fire bolts that Break enemy Armour. Can fire a limited number of bolts before needing to reload.
ArmourPiercingBoltsPlayer.name: Armour Piercing Rounds

ArtilleryBallistaPlayer.description: Deploy a Ballista Totem that fires bolts skyward, to explode a short time after landing.
ArtilleryBallistaPlayer.name: Artillery Ballista

AttritionPlayer.description: While active, causes you to deal more Hit damage to Rare and Unique enemies the longer you've been fighting them, and gain Culling Strike against them once you've been fighting them for long enough.
AttritionPlayer.name: Attrition

BerserkPlayer.description: While active, strengthens your Rage and grants you Life Leech based on your Rage, but causes you to lose Life while Raging.
BerserkPlayer.name: Berserk

BoneshatterPlayer.description: Attack enemies with a melee Strike. The Strike will cause a Heavy Stun on enemies that are Primed for Stun. Upon causing a Heavy Stun it will also create a Shockwave, dealing a large amount of damage in an area.
BoneshatterPlayer.name: Boneshatter

ClusterGrenadePlayer.description: Fire a bouncing Grenade that explodes when its fuse expires, throwing out a nova of mini Grenades that explode when they come to a stop.
ClusterGrenadePlayer.name: Cluster Grenade

DefianceBannerReservationPlayer.description: While active, killing enemies with Attacks or standing near a Unique enemy generates Valour. Using this Skill consumes its Valour to place an inspiring Banner with an Aura that grants you and nearby Allies Armour, Evasion and movement speed while the Banner lasts. The Banner cannot gain Valour while placed, and you cannot place a Banner while you already have a Banner placed.
DefianceBannerReservationPlayer.name: Defiance Banner

DreadBannerReservationPlayer.description: While active, killing enemies with Attacks or standing near a Unique enemy generates Valour. Using this Skill consumes its Valour to place an inspiring Banner with an Aura that grants you and nearby Allies Stun Threshold, Elemental Ailment Threshold and Flask charges while the Banner lasts. The Banner cannot gain Valour while placed, and you cannot place a Banner while you already have a Banner placed.
DreadBannerReservationPlayer.name: Dread Banner

EarthquakePlayer.description: Smash the ground, dealing damage in an area and leaving behind Jagged Ground that slows enemies. The Jagged Ground erupts in a powerful Aftershock after a duration. Cannot create Jagged Ground on top of an existing patch, or if you already have the maximum number of active patches.
EarthquakePlayer.name: Earthquake

EarthshatterPlayer.description: Slam the ground, sending out a fissure that deals area damage to enemies it passes under and thrusts a spike from the ground when it ends. Warcries performed near the spike will cause it to shatter, damaging surrounding enemies.
EarthshatterPlayer.name: Earthshatter

EmergencyReloadPlayer.description: Instantly reload your active Crossbow Ammunition and Empowers the loaded bolts to deal more damage.
EmergencyReloadPlayer.name: Emergency Reload

ExplosiveGrenadePlayer.description: Fire a bouncing Grenade that unleashes a devastating fiery blast when its fuse expires.
ExplosiveGrenadePlayer.name: Explosive Grenade

ExplosiveShotAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with flaming bolts that explode on impact. The explosion will cause any Grenades in its area of effect to also explode.
ExplosiveShotAmmoPlayer.name: Load Explosive Shot

ExplosiveShotPlayer.description: Fire a flaming bolt that explodes on impact. The explosion will cause any Grenades in its area of effect to also explode.
ExplosiveShotPlayer.name: Explosive Shot

ExsanguinatePlayer.description: Expel your own blood as Chaining blood tendrils in a cone in front of you. Enemies hit by the tendrils take Physical damage and are inflicted with a Debuff that deals Physical damage over time.
ExsanguinatePlayer.name: Exsanguinate

FlashGrenadePlayer.description: Fire a bouncing Grenade that unleashes a Blinding, Stunning explosion when its fuse expires.
FlashGrenadePlayer.name: Flash Grenade

FragmentationRoundsAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with Piercing bolts that fragment in flight. Bolts that hit a Frozen enemy consume the Freeze and cause an explosion of shrapnel. Bolts that hit an Ice Crystal cause it to explode.
FragmentationRoundsAmmoPlayer.name: Load Fragmentation Rounds

FragmentationRoundsPlayer.description: Fire Piercing bolts that fragment in flight. Bolts that hit a Frozen enemy Consume the Freeze and cause an explosion of shrapnel. Bolts that hit an Ice Crystal cause it to explode.
FragmentationRoundsPlayer.name: Fragmentation Rounds

GalvanicShardsAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with a clip of charged bolts that fragment in flight, releasing Chaining Lightning beams when they Hit enemies. Using this skill again reloads the clip.
GalvanicShardsAmmoPlayer.name: Load Galvanic Shards

GalvanicShardsPlayer.description: Rapidly fire charged bolts that fragment in flight, releasing Chaining Lightning beams when they Hit enemies. Can fire a limited number of bursts before needing to reload.
GalvanicShardsPlayer.name: Galvanic Shards

GlacialBoltAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with icy bolts that create two walls of Ice Crystals at the end of their flight.
GlacialBoltAmmoPlayer.name: Load Glacial Bolt

GlacialBoltPlayer.description: Fire an icy bolt that creates two walls of Ice Crystals at the end of its flight.
GlacialBoltPlayer.name: Glacial Bolt

HailstormRoundsAmmoPlayer.description: Passively generate bolts of ice at a frequency equal to reload time, up to a cap. Activate to Load the accumulated bolts into your Crossbow. All loaded bolts are fired at once, causing them to rain down over the target area.
HailstormRoundsAmmoPlayer.name: Load Hailstorm Rounds

HailstormRoundsPlayer.description: Fire all loaded bolts into the sky, causing them to rain down over the target area.
HailstormRoundsPlayer.name: Hailstorm Rounds

HammerOfTheGodsPlayer.description: Build Glory by Heavy Stunning enemies. When you have maximum Glory you may entreat the Ancestors to crush your enemies, manifesting a massive hammer that falls from the sky onto your target, Slamming into the ground after a short duration and dealing immense damage based on your weapon.
HammerOfTheGodsPlayer.name: Hammer of the Gods

HeraldOfAshPlayer.description: While active, enemies you sufficiently Overkill with non-Herald Attacks will cause an explosion that Ignites nearby enemies based on the Overkill damage dealt.
HeraldOfAshPlayer.name: Herald of Ash

HeraldOfBloodPlayer.description: While active, killing an enemy with Blood Loss will cause a bloody explosion that deals Physical Attack damage to surrounding enemies based off the life of the exploded enemy, destroying their Corpse if the enemy was Normal or Magic. The explosion also has a chance to Aggravate Bleeding.
HeraldOfBloodPlayer.name: Herald of Blood

HighVelocityRoundsAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with Piercing bolts that can consume Fully Broken Armour on enemies to deal extra damage.
HighVelocityRoundsAmmoPlayer.name: Load High Velocity Rounds

HighVelocityRoundsPlayer.description: Fire a powerful Piercing bolt that can consume Fully Broken Armour on enemies to deal extra damage.
HighVelocityRoundsPlayer.name: High Velocity Rounds

IceShardsAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with a clip of icy bolts that rapidly fire at the ground, leaving a shard of ice at the impact location unless the bolt hits an enemy. The ice shards shatter when enemies step on them, dealing damage to nearby enemies. Using this skill again reloads the clip.
IceShardsAmmoPlayer.name: Load Ice Shards

IceShardsPlayer.description: Rapidly fire icy bolts at the ground, leaving a shard of ice at the impact location unless the bolt hits an enemy. The ice shards shatter when enemies step on them, dealing damage to nearby enemies. Can fire a limited number of bolts before needing to reload.
IceShardsPlayer.name: Ice Shards

IncendiaryShotAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with flaming bolts that fragment in flight, damaging and Igniting enemies on hit and in a small cone behind their final target.
IncendiaryShotAmmoPlayer.name: Load Incendiary Shot

IncendiaryShotPlayer.description: Fire flaming bolts that fragment in flight, damaging and Igniting enemies on hit, and in a small cone behind their final target.
IncendiaryShotPlayer.name: Incendiary Shot

InfernalCryCorpseExplosionPlayer.description: The enemy's Corpse violently explodes, dealing Fire damage in an area around it.
InfernalCryCorpseExplosionPlayer.name: Combust

InfernalCryPlayer.description: Perform a warcry, Empowering subsequent Attacks. Consumes all Endurance Charges to Empower additional attacks. Enemies in the warcry's area are destabilised and will Combust on death.
InfernalCryPlayer.name: Infernal Cry

LeapSlamPlayer.description:
Jump into the air, damaging and Knocking Back enemies with your mace where you land. Enemies you would land on are
pushed out of the way.
LeapSlamPlayer.name: Leap Slam

MagmaBarrierPlayer.description: When you raise your Shield it is infused with magma for a short time. Blocking during this time will spray magma at the attacker and grant you an Endurance Charge.
MagmaBarrierPlayer.name: Magma Barrier

MetaCastLightningSpellOnHitPlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you Hit enemies with Melee Attacks and triggers socketed Lightning spells on reaching maximum Energy.
MetaCastLightningSpellOnHitPlayer.name: Lightning Spell on Melee Hit

MetaCastOnBlockPlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you Block and triggers socketed Spells on reaching maximum Energy.
MetaCastOnBlockPlayer.name: Cast on Block

MetaCastOnMeleeKillPlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you kill enemies with Melee Attacks and triggers socketed spells on reaching maximum Energy.
MetaCastOnMeleeKillPlayer.name: Cast on Melee Kill

MetaCastOnMeleeStunPlayer.description: While active, gains Energy when you Stun enemies with Melee Attacks and triggers socketed spells on reaching maximum Energy.
MetaCastOnMeleeStunPlayer.name: Cast on Melee Stun

MoltenBlastPlayer.description: Gouge molten rock from the ground and fling it at the target. The Projectile explodes on collision, damaging enemies and scattering shrapnel in a cone behind it.
MoltenBlastPlayer.name: Molten Blast

OilGrenadePlayer.description: Fire a bouncing Grenade that bursts in a spray of Oil when the fuse expires or when it impacts an Enemy, dealing minimal damage but covering the ground and nearby enemies in Oil. Oil created this way can be Ignited by Detonator Skills or Ignited Ground.
OilGrenadePlayer.name: Oil Grenade

OverwhelmingPresencePlayer.description: While active, emits an Aura that makes enemies in your Presence easier to Stun and inflict Elemental Ailments upon.
OverwhelmingPresencePlayer.name: Overwhelming Presence

PerfectStrikePlayer.description: Charge up your weapon while channelling. Releasing the moment you fully charge will release a wave of Fire.
PerfectStrikePlayer.name: Perfect Strike

PermafrostBoltsAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with icy bolts that fragment in flight, damaging enemies on hit and in a small cone behind their final target. The icy coating on the bolts makes them extremely potent at Freezing enemies.
PermafrostBoltsAmmoPlayer.name: Load Permafrost Bolts

PermafrostBoltsPlayer.description: Fire icy bolts that  fragment in flight, damaging enemies on hit and in a small cone behind their final target. The icy coating on the bolts makes them extremely potent at Freezing enemies.
PermafrostBoltsPlayer.name: Permafrost Bolts

PlasmaBlastAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with unstable bolts that require a lengthy charging period to fire but deal devastating damage, Pierce through enemies, and explode upon hitting terrain. Additional Projectiles are fired in a spread, unlike other Crossbow Skills.
PlasmaBlastAmmoPlayer.name: Load Plasma Blast

PlasmaBlastPlayer.description: Channel to charge an unstable bolt. The bolt deals devastating damage and explodes on hitting terrain, but cannot be fired at all unless fully charged. Additional Projectiles are fired in a spread, unlike other Crossbow Skills.
PlasmaBlastPlayer.name: Plasma Blast

RapidShotAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with a large clip of heavily modified bolts that cause Heat to build up on your crossbow, before unleashing a stream of flaming bolts that gain Fire Damage based on your Heat. Heat also grants bonus damage to Grenades you fire, but dissipates rapidly when not building up. Using this skill again reloads the clip.
RapidShotAmmoPlayer.name: Load Rapid Shot

RapidShotPlayer.description: Fire heavily modified bolts that cause Heat to build up on your crossbow. Using this skill causes an initial buildup of Heat before unleashing a stream of flaming bolts that gain Fire Damage based on your Heat. Heat also grants bonus damage to Grenades you fire, but dissipates rapidly when not building up. Can fire a large number of bolts before needing to reload.
RapidShotPlayer.name: Rapid Shot

ReapPlayer.description: Conjure a bloody scythe that sweeps across the targeted area, dealing Physical damage to enemies and applying Critical Weakness.
ReapPlayer.name: Reap

ResonatingShieldPlayer.description: Repeatedly hammer your Shield with your weapon causing damaging shockwaves in an area around you. Enemies hit by the shockwave lose Armour for a duration. While using Resonating Shield, your Shield is raised and you will Block all incoming Blockable hits.
ResonatingShieldPlayer.name: Resonating Shield

RipwireBallistaPlayer.description: Deploy a Ballista Totem that fires Pinning bolts which Maim Enemies.
RipwireBallistaPlayer.name: Ripwire Ballista

RollingSlamPlayer.description: Slam the ground to Stun enemies and knock them away, then continue forward and perform a devastating second Slam. Holding down the skill input allows you to change direction as you move.
RollingSlamPlayer.name: Rolling Slam

ScavengedPlatingPlayer.description: While active, uses fragments of armour scavenged from enemies to bolster your own. Fully Breaking an enemy's Armour grants you stacks of Scavenged Plating for a duration based on the enemy's rarity, and you gain Armour and Thorns per stack. Normal enemies grant 1 stack, Magic enemies grant 2 stacks, Rare enemies grant 5 stacks and Unique enemies grant 10 stacks.
ScavengedPlatingPlayer.name: Scavenged Plating

SeismicCryPlayer.description: Perform a damaging warcry, Knocking Back nearby enemies. If a Heavy Stunned enemy is hit, your next Slam is Empowered to perform an additional Aftershock. If not, this skill's cooldown is reset. Only counts Heavily Stunned enemies for purposes of counting Power Gained.
SeismicCryPlayer.name: Seismic Cry

ShardScavengerPlayer.description: While active, Consuming Freeze, Shock, Ignite, or Fully Broken Armour on an enemy reloads your Crossbow, restores one cooldown use for your Grenades and grants a Buff causing Crossbow Attacks to not consume bolts for a duration. This can only occur once every few seconds.
ShardScavengerPlayer.name: Shard Scavenger

ShieldChargePlayer.description: Channel to charge in the target direction. You will crash into enemies on your path, stopping your charge and dealing damage to enemies in an area, and extra damage to the enemies you collided with. While charging, your Shield is raised and you will Block all incoming Blockable hits.
ShieldChargePlayer.name: Shield Charge

ShieldWallPlayer.description: Ram your Shield into the ground, throwing up a semi-circular wall of earth. Enemies can attack the walls and your Slams or Warcries will instantly destroy them. Each wall segment explodes when destroyed, damaging enemies around it.
ShieldWallPlayer.name: Shield Wall

ShockGrenadePlayer.description: Fire a bouncing Grenade that discharges an Electrocuting Lightning blast when its fuse expires.
ShockGrenadePlayer.name: Voltaic Grenade

ShockburstRoundsAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with a clip of charged bolts which release damaging pulses upon Hitting an enemy affected by a Lightning Ailment. Using this skill again reloads the clip.
ShockburstRoundsAmmoPlayer.name: Load Shockburst Rounds

ShockburstRoundsPlayer.description: Rapidly fire charged bolts which release damaging pulses upon Hitting an enemy affected by a Lightning Ailment. Can fire a limited number of bolts before needing to reload.
ShockburstRoundsPlayer.name: Shockburst Rounds

ShockwaveTotemPlayer.description: Raise a Totem that Slams the ground around it, repeatedly damaging nearby enemies. Jagged Ground erupts when hit by this Slam, damaging enemies standing on it.
ShockwaveTotemPlayer.name: Shockwave Totem

SiegeCascadeAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with enemy-seeking payloads which are fired into the air, dropping a bolt near every enemy in the target area. These bolts lodge in the ground and explode after a short delay.
SiegeCascadeAmmoPlayer.name: Load Siege Cascade

SiegeCascadePlayer.description: Aim skyward and fires an enemy-seeking payload which drops a bolt near every enemy in the target area. These bolts lodge in the ground and explode after a short delay.
SiegeCascadePlayer.name: Siege Cascade

StaffConsecratePlayer.description: Create an area of Consecrated Ground around you.
StaffConsecratePlayer.name: Consecrate

StampedePlayer.description: Charges forward, cracking the earth and leaving a patch of Jagged Ground with every footstep. At the end of your charge, a massive leaping Slam damages enemies and causes all nearby patches of Jagged Ground to explode, damaging enemies standing on them.
StampedePlayer.name: Stampede

StormblastBoltsAmmoPlayer.description: Load your Crossbow with charged bolts that land around the target location and explode if hit by a Detonator Skill. Using this skill again reloads the clip.
StormblastBoltsAmmoPlayer.name: Load Stormblast Bolts

StormblastBoltsPlayer.description: Aims skyward and fires charged bolts that land around the target location, dealing damage and lodging in the ground for a duration. Detonator Skills will cause these bolts to explode. Can fire a limited number of bolts before needing to reload.
StormblastBoltsPlayer.name: Stormblast Bolts

SunderPlayer.description: Slam the ground, creating a roiling fissure that damages enemies in a sequence of areas in front of you. A number of enemies hit by the wave will release a shockwave, damaging other enemies.
SunderPlayer.name: Sunder

SuperchargedSlamPlayer.description: Channel to charge up a heavy swing, drawing earth from the ground to enlarge your mace. Release to Slam the ground, dealing damage in an area around the impact, followed by Aftershocks dealing damage in a larger area.
SuperchargedSlamPlayer.name: Supercharged Slam

TimeOfNeedPlayer.description: While active, periodically invokes divine blessings to heal you and remove Curses and Elemental Ailments from you.
TimeOfNeedPlayer.name: Time of Need

ToxicGrenadePlayer.description: Fire a bouncing Grenade that causes a burst of Poison gas when its fuse expires, damaging enemies and leaving behind a growing Poison cloud. Burning effects or Detonator skills will cause the cloud to explode in a fiery blast.
ToxicGrenadePlayer.name: Gas Grenade

VolcanicFissurePlayer.description: Slam the ground, creating a winding fissure that deals damage as it travels and remains for a duration. Using a different Slam on a fissure will cause an Aftershock, which spreads to all connected fissures.
VolcanicFissurePlayer.name: Volcanic Fissure

WarBannerReservationPlayer.description: While active, killing enemies with Attacks or standing near a Unique enemy generates Valour. Using this Skill consumes its Valour to place an inspiring Banner with an Aura that grants you and nearby Allies Attack damage and Accuracy while the Banner lasts. The Banner cannot gain Valour while placed, and you cannot place a Banner while you already have a Banner placed.
WarBannerReservationPlayer.name: War Banner
